What SpokenBits LLC. is an early stage technology startup founded in the heart of Silicon Valley. We have a grand vision about our product, but for now the SpokenBits iOS Application allows you to give it any of your favorite articles or blog posts' URLs (in any language), and it will extract the uncluttered context from it and read it for you. Think of it as mini Audio Book of your favorite articles or blog posts.

Why We the founders love reading a good article or blog post, and it was hard to keep up with our always increasing queue of articles. Then we thought "what if I could listen to these articles during my commute ?". As you can imagine, we are scratching our own itch with the SpokenBits iOS Application, and we've been using and loving it since the very early prototypes. We hope you find it useful too.

Who SpokenBits was founded by three guys who have been developing software for many years and have worked on multiple companies like: Oracle, Symantec, Rearden Commerce (Deem), Palm, Motorola and BEA Systems to mention a few.
